<h1 id="kopano-rest-api">Kopano Rest API</h1>
<p>it is recommended to install the kopano api playground to do quick tests.</p>
<p>The source of the playground is available at: https://stash.kopano.io/projects/KC/repos/kapi/browse/examples</p>
<p>A pre compiled version can be downloaded from https://nextcloud.kopano.com/index.php/s/V3KbNsQDT9VMduQ</p>
<p>After extracting it to /var/www/kapi-playground you can call it like the following:</p>
<p>Call it e.g. with https://@%<span class="citation">@hostname</span>@%@.@%<span class="citation">@domainname</span>@%@/kapi-playground/?iss=https://@%<span class="citation">@hostname</span>@%@.@%<span class="citation">@domainname</span>@%@</p>
